properties.text:
[color=#a5a1b4]PIERCE SHOT[/color]

Your arrows [color=#a5a1b4]PIERCE[/color], allowing you to hit multiple enemies with the same arrow.

[color=#a5a1b4]CHARGED SHOT[/color]

Stand still and [color=#a5a1b4]HOLD FIRE[/color] to charge up your shot, inflicting extra damage.

[color=#a5a1b4]MULTISHOT[/color]

Shoot three arrows in a cone in front of you at the same time.

[color=#00f1f2]FROST ARROWS[/color]

Attacks can cause [color=#00f1f2]EMBRITTLEMENT[/color]: enemies take extra arrow damage.

[color=#FF0000]FIRE ARROWS[/color]

Attacks inflict [color=#FF0000]BURN[/color] damage over time to enemies hit by them.

[color=#f2e600]ELECTRIC ARROWS[/color]


[color=#f2e600]SHOCK[/color] enemies and spread damage to enemies nearby.
